  "title": "The 11 O'clock Number",
  "description": "The 11 O’clock Number is Grindstone’s award winning improvised musical comedy! Based on suggestions from the audience the cast improvises a brand new musical comedy on the spot, complete with twisting plots and showstopping numbers. Laughs are guaranteed. You have to see it to believe it.",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Byron Martin, Mhairi Berg and Simon Abbott<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Simon Abbott, Mhairi Berg, Curtis Den Otter, Evan Dowling, Sarah Dowling, Dallas Friesen, Donna Leny Hansen, Katie Hudson, Byron Martin, Erin Maxwell, Wilmari Myburgh, Jaimi Reese, Logan Teske, Abby Vandenberghe, Malachi Wilkins, Stephanie Wolfe<br/>",
